---
// Opção 5: Checklist de diagnóstico — problemas do site atual vs Anúncio e Site
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 bg-transparent overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-500 mb-8">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="font-medium">Nota Máxima no Google Pagespeed</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6 leading-tight font-['Outfit']">
        O Site Que Transforma Seus Anúncios em <span class="text-[#6366F1]">Clientes no WhatsApp</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
        Nossa infraestrutura garante que nenhuma oportunidade seja perdida. Substituímos seu site lento por uma estrutura focada em uma única coisa: fazer seu telefone tocar.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center lg:justify-start justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl py-3 px-5 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400 whitespace-nowrap">5 em 10</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300 text-center sm:text-left">clientes perdidos por sites lentos <span class="text-zinc-500">(Google)</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="#planos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base px-8 py-4 bg-[#6366F1] text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(99,102,241,0.4)] transition-all">
          Ver Planos
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M7 1l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Direita: Checklist diagnóstico -->
    <div class="relative w-full mt-8 lg:mt-0">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl">

        <!-- Coluna Antes -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Seu site atual provavelmente...</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Demora mais de 3 segundos para abrir',
              'Não tem botão de WhatsApp visível',
              'Tem menus que distraem o visitante',
              'Perde mais da metade dos acessos no celular',
            ].map(item => (
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3.5 bg-red-500/5 border border-red-900/20 rounded-xl">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                  <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.3" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <path d="M5 5l6 6M11 5l-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-snug">{item}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-700 to-transparent my-5"></div>

        <!-- Coluna Depois -->
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[#6366F1] uppercase tracking-widest">Com Anúncio e Site</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Abre em menos de 1 segundo no celular',
              'Botão de WhatsApp sempre visível e fixo',
            ].map(item => (
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3.5 bg-[#6366F1]/5 border border-[#6366F1]/20 rounded-xl">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#6366F1] mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                  <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.3" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-200 leading-snug">{item}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
